For example: bearaabear
Here for the first bear we will find 8 substring. Like
bear
beara
bearaa
bearaab
bearaabe
bearaabea
bearaabear
bearaabearc

The main thing is for the first bear we will find all possible substring so we will not count next time for it. If we find any bear as substring in next we will start making 
substring from e not from b. Because we made all substring for b.
"emrulbearhasanbear"
In this example, for the first bear we will make all substring including its previous characters also like emrul. So, if next time we find bear as substring we will start
conting from e right after b not from starting e. Beacuse we ccounted substring for e, m, r, u, l as well as b. 


